Fed’s Lockhart Sees ‘High Bar’ for Any Post-June Bond Buying

-- B y   C a r o l i n e   S a l a s   a n d   D a v i d   B e a s l e y
-- 
2011-05-05T01:01:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/fed-s-lockhart-sees-high-bar-for-any-post-june-bond-buying.html
Federal Reserve Bank of Atlanta
President  Dennis Lockhart  said there would be a high hurdle for
the start of more asset purchases after the central bank
finishes buying $600 billion of  Treasury securities  in June.  “There really is a high bar for implementing a new
program,” Lockhart said in response to questions from reporters
after a speech in Atlanta.  To contact the reporter on this story:
